Bishop Issac Idahosa of God First Ministries, Ajah has put smiles on the faces of the poor in his church and vicinity by giving them free foodstuff like bags of rice, cash, and hand sanitisers to cushion the effect of the lockdown. Idahosa, who was ably supported by some Nollywood practitioners such as Keppy Ekpeyong Bassey, Chico Ejiro among others, gave out such items as bags of rice, provision, hand sanitisers, toiletries with words of encouragement advising them to obey laid down rules by government concerning the Coronavirus and try to be safe. He also suspended offering of any type while urging them to use the money to feed at this trying time.